170
00:18:05.292 --> 00:18:07.586
<font color="white">Right here! Let me off here.</font><font color="white"></font>

171
00:18:07.669 --> 00:18:08.962
<font color="white">Yes. right here.</font><font color="white"></font>

172
00:18:09.046 --> 00:18:10.506
