178
00:18:28.732 --> 00:18:29.733
<font color="white">What's going on?</font><font color="white"></font>

179
00:18:31.110 --> 00:18:32.027
<font color="white">That punk…</font><font color="white"></font>

180
00:18:32.111 --> 00:18:33.445
