184
00:18:38.784 --> 00:18:40.494
<font color="white">Let me talk first! Hey!</font><font color="white"></font>

185
00:18:40.577 --> 00:18:42.871
<font color="white">What's going on?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">What happened to Min-ji? Where is she?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

186
00:18:42.955 --> 00:18:43.789
<font color="white">Who are these bastards?</font><font color="white"></font>

187
00:18:43.872 --> 00:18:45.040
<font color="white">Who are they?!</font><font color="white"></font>

188
00:18:45.124 --> 00:18:46.959
<font color="white">Who the hell…</font><font color="white"></font>

189
00:18:47.042 --> 00:18:48.669
<font color="white">Who are these damn bastards?!</font><font color="white"></font>

190
00:18:48.752 --> 00:18:50.379
<font color="white">They're dead meat!</font><font color="white"></font>

191
00:18:50.462 --> 00:18:51.421
<font color="white">Damn it!</font><font color="white"></font>

192
00:18:51.505 --> 00:18:53.340
<font color="white">-Hey. is it okay if I break this?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Careful with that!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

193
