<font color="white">Goddamn it!</font><font color="white"></font>

194
00:18:55.968 --> 00:18:58.428
<font color="white">I'm good. Let's focus now.</font><font color="white"></font>

195
00:18:58.512 --> 00:18:59.805
<font color="white">Hey. are you okay?</font><font color="white"></font>

196
00:18:59.888 --> 00:19:00.889
<font color="white">Are you…</font><font color="white"></font>

197
00:19:00.973 --> 00:19:02.057
<font color="white">Hey!</font><font color="white"></font>

198
00:19:02.141 --> 00:19:03.934
<font color="white">You already got attacked?!</font><font color="white"></font>

199
00:19:04.017 --> 00:19:05.144
<font color="white">That's a gunshot wound. right?</font><font color="white"></font>

200
00:19:05.227 --> 00:19:07.104
<font color="white">I told you to be careful!</font><font color="white"></font>

201
00:19:07.187 --> 00:19:10.023
<font color="white">What were you two going to do without me?</font><font color="white"></font>

202
00:19:11.775 --> 00:19:13.110
<font color="white">I'm here now. so don't worry.</font><font color="white"></font>

203
00:19:13.694 --> 00:19:14.736
<font color="white">Don't worry.</font><font color="white"></font>

204
00:19:15.237 --> 00:19:16.238
<font color="white">Just think of it</font><font color="white"></font>

205
00:19:16.321 --> 00:19:18.907
