208
00:19:25.539 --> 00:19:27.416
<font color="white">I'm just saying.</font><font color="white"></font>

209
00:19:27.499 --> 00:19:29.835
<font color="white">Come on. we've been shot at before!</font><font color="white"></font>

210
00:19:29.918 --> 00:19:30.794
<font color="white">Just keep driving.</font><font color="white"></font>

211
00:19:31.628 --> 00:19:32.713
<font color="white">Are you okay?</font><font color="white"></font>

212
00:19:33.463 --> 00:19:34.840
<font color="white">By the way. where are we going?</font><font color="white"></font>

213
00:19:34.923 --> 00:19:36.925
<font color="white">Hwasin Station to find a homeless guy.</font><font color="white"></font>

214
00:19:37.009 --> 00:19:39.052
<font color="white">The homeless guy who found Min-ji's phone.</font><font color="white"></font>

215
00:19:39.136 --> 00:19:42.431
