217
00:19:45.392 --> 00:19:47.436
<font color="white">8-3. Gongdan-gil. Seonmin-eup.</font><font color="white"></font>

218
00:19:47.519 --> 00:19:48.812
<font color="white">Park Jin-cheol has joined them.</font><font color="white"></font>

219
00:19:56.111 --> 00:19:57.738
<font color="white">-Step on it.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Yes. sir.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

220
00:20:04.745 --> 00:20:05.579
<font color="white">Hey.</font><font color="white"></font>

221
00:20:06.830 --> 00:20:07.706
<font color="white">Let's hurry.</font><font color="white"></font>

222
00:20:11.376 --> 00:20:12.211
<font color="white">Hey. you.</font><font color="white"></font>

223
00:20:13.670 --> 00:20:15.255
<font color="white">Go buy me a bottle of soju.</font><font color="white"></font>

224
00:20:15.339 --> 00:20:17.007
<font color="white">Damn it. Why aren't you going?</font><font color="white"></font>

225
00:20:17.925 --> 00:20:19.676
<font color="white">Want me to teach you a lesson. you punk?</font><font color="white"></font>

226
00:20:20.302 --> 00:20:21.720
<font color="white">-Dad!</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Come here!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

227
00:20:22.304 --> 00:20:23.347
<font color="white">-You little punk.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-What's wrong?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

228
